  "summary": "Malicious code in notify-theme (npm)",
  "details": "Notify-theme@1.3.5 is a trojanized clone of the pino logger. When the package is required, index.js spawns a detached child process running lib/caller.js. That file fetches a payload from hxxps://jsonkeeper[.]com/b/EXSIF via axios and executes the response as arbitrary JavaScript code using the Function constructor, enabling remote code execution on the installer's machine. The C2 URL is hardcoded at jsonkeeper[.]com/b/EXSIF.",
